There is a 10*10 grid which is textured as land

Randomly some cubes are absent (hollow space)

Randomly some cubes move up & down (fire texture)

Player starts at left bottom (orange texture).(Arrow keys control movement)

Destination is top right corner (textured as a crown).

Water surrounds the game play.

There are following views:

1 Default view (by an altitude)
2 Tower view (from top of board)
3 Chase Cam (follows the player)

These views can be toggled while playing (T-Tower , C- Chase Cam ,E-Default)

Also the board can be zoomed into & zoomed out. (F-to go far N- To come near)

And also the default cam can be adjusted.(W-increase angle S-decrease angle)
